{"nodes":[{"pos":[11,42],"content":"DSC Class Resource Improvements","needQuote":true,"nodes":[{"content":"DSC Class Resource Improvements","pos":[0,31]}]},{"content":"DSC Class Resource Improvements","pos":[89,120]},{"content":"In this release, we have fixed following know issues from WMF 5.0:","pos":[122,188]},{"content":"Get-DscConfiguration may return empty values (null) or errors if a complex/hashtable type is returned by Get() function of a class based DSC resource.","pos":[191,341]},{"content":"Get-DscConfiguration returns error if RunAs credential is used in DSC Configuration.","pos":[344,428]},{"content":"Class based resource cannot be used in a Composite Configuration.","pos":[431,496]},{"content":"Start-DscConfiguration hangs if Class based resource has a property of its own type.","pos":[499,583]},{"content":"Class based resource cannot be used as an exclusive resource.","pos":[586,647]}],"content":"---\ntitle: DSC Class Resource Improvements\nauthor:  jaimeo\ncontributor: amitsara\n---\n\n## DSC Class Resource Improvements\n\nIn this release, we have fixed following know issues from WMF 5.0:\n* Get-DscConfiguration may return empty values (null) or errors if a complex/hashtable type is returned by Get() function of a class based DSC resource.\n* Get-DscConfiguration returns error if RunAs credential is used in DSC Configuration.\n* Class based resource cannot be used in a Composite Configuration.\n* Start-DscConfiguration hangs if Class based resource has a property of its own type.\n* Class based resource cannot be used as an exclusive resource.\n"}